git init       step1
git status  (optional)
git add file or path (step 2)
git remote add origin <https://github.com/username/projectname>.git (copy from the webpage)    (step 3)
git commit -m "initial-commit" (step 4)     if fails , do follow the highlighted steps ........ else follow step 5
