git clone <URL of the project>                                              // for copying the project from the github of a specific user

git add .   				// for addding all the files to the repository.

=======================================branches====================================================

git checkout -b <branchName>            //creates new branch  and move to new Created branch.

git checkout <branchName>		//change the working branch to given branch

git push origin <branchName>

